author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! Today we look at a youtuber from Italy who recently got raided for having a few consoles in his house. These consoles contained roms of games he showcased in his videos and if the law applies, he could face jail time. This is the worst response to piracy I've seen and completely ignores the real facilitators. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Going To Prison Over Video Game ROMs...
